reviewText: Great accounts of White House employees over the years. It was very informative filled with first person accounts from the employees.

THIS DVD IS AWESOME!  AFTER SEEING THE MOVIE "THE BUTLER" I WANTED MORE INFORMATION...WELL I GOT IT ON THIS DVD.  PRESIDENT JIMMY CARTER DID AN OUTSTANDING JOB OF INTRODUCING PART OF THE WHITE HOUSE STAFF.  TRULY EDUCATIONAL AND ENJOYABLE.
What an Awesome historical collection of fact's, interviews and history that this DVD brings you. I have already watched it twice and will watch it again!!!
